channel.title: Yozy's Extra Tracks
channel.description:
Tell me if this is in the wrong category.
These are extras that I made for fun, my discontinued tracks, or anything I made that was never given a core purpose.
**We Are The Champions Melody Remix** https://app.auxy.co/projects/orGWxFFXoYDo0AygIlxp7w== Made in 5 minutes, when my friends were talking about the original song.
**Discontinued** https://app.auxy.co/projects/A8tHKG-prsf11bHRao1EnA== A track that was discontinued and eventually evolved into one of my favorite tracks, Electric Heights.
**The Land of Boggs** https://app.auxy.co/projects/aX8MntOatedd0arKRMBOIg== A recreation of one of the melodies used in The Land of Boggs shorts (made without affiliation).
**Spray Factory** https://app.auxy.co/projects/71QvPKUwfFf5NoY3DxyOVA== A fun little track I made during my first period one day. It mainly uses the instrument "Spray", hence the name.
**Sci-Fi Facility** https://app.auxy.co/projects/7slAq4_7LHSjpf-OLrPnOA== The track was later remastered as Sci-Fi Center and used in Flash Flood 2's OST. It was a track I made for fun that I made while having Flash Flood 2 in mind, but never intended to make a map for it. I did make a FF2 map for the track after it was remastered.
